reviews.review_text: Many great moments including d3t01.flac actually The Handsome Cabin Boy "jam"(Shady Grove - Track 11).  Thanks for this high quality recording. A must-have for the 1993 time period.
spring 1993 set list from hell,shakedown/wang dang doodle set two playin/dark star the other one and lucy in the sky with diamonds just killer!
